e.", "Eriksson mener det ikke er spesielt dyrt om man er mange som deler p\u00e5 regningen. Hun forteller at de f\u00e5r mange henvendelser fra Norge og at leietakerne s\u00e5 langt har variert mellom bedrifter og privatpersoner."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|utenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "7ce3957b80bf11c9ff8fc834872275c67b291167ebaae44c14fd93a2650c211b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2012-08-16T20:00:45.081Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "N\u00e5 kan du leie \u00abThe Villa\u00bb. - Jeg har brukt altfor mye penger p\u00e5 den, sier Stordalen til adressa.no."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1372756.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/villaarticle10"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/dee7079359075f2ffec04348ee0b1bd4701c63ea.jpg?5970ce8f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Her er Stordalens luksushytte i \u00c5re -adressa.no", "Forrige eiers villadr\u00f8m", "- Har det for tavelt", "40 000 - 100 000 kroner per d\u00f8gn"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "dee7079359075f2ffec04348ee0b1bd4701c63ea"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "utenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "real-estate"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["forrige eiers", "villa", "leie"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["copperhill mountain lodge", "the villa", "stordalen", "st. mortiz"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "aspen", "\u00e5re"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "ulrika eriksson"}, {"field": "k